snippet.title: Lemmings: Fujitsu FM Towns (1992)
snippet.description:
Intro and gameplay from Lemmings on the Fujitsu FM Towns, released in 1992.
Developed by DMA Design and published by Imagineer

Game credits:
- Brian Johnston - Music
- Dave Jones - Code
- Gary Timmons - Animation
- Scott Johnston - Graphics
- Tim Wright - Music
- Taizou Kojima - Code
- Takashi Ohtani - Code (Music)
- Yasutoshi Ishida - Director

Watch other editions of the Lemmings game here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW_a1Ic-Y4n_sYe2n1OCwe0j03EOxxq3U

Enjoy the video? Remember to like, comment and subscribe to Retro Gaming TV - http://bit.ly/2N5gjMA
